        <div><p>I may be getting older and much more cantankerous â€“Â it's been the second year in a row when I don't get the Christmas-New Year season. It's almost annoying.</p>
<p>And the New Year used to be my favourite holiday â€“ getting all together with my family, having the celebration exclusive dishes cooked by my mother and my ants, writing letters to Santa Claus with my cousins, and getting reasonable gifts â€“ it all used to make sense.</p>
